What you need to know:  Kadivane says his long-term goal is to graduate to the Kenya National Rally Championship but his car is not eligible for competition as per the FIA homologation rules until recentlyThe Kenya Motorsports Federation Chairman Phineas Kimathi formed a taskforce to look into ways to increase entries in the 2023 national competitions and rope in drivers like KadivaneA new competition structure of 13 classes has been introduced and the overall national champion title scrapped